    <h1 class="mb-4">The Story of MLAB</h1>
    <p>
      The origins of MLAB date back to around 2004 when Milan Horkel (MiHo), a professional hardware developer, designed the first module, 
      <a href="https://www.mlab.cz/module/RS232SINGLE01/" target="_blank">RS232SINGLE01</a>. His vision was to create an open, robust, and universal technical kit suitable for both hobbyists and professionals. The goal was to provide a reliable and flexible tool for testing and developing new, often revolutionary devices.
    </p>
