    <h2 class="mt-5">Early Development</h2>
    <p>
      Soon, Milan was joined by Martin Kákona (<a href="https://github.com/kakl" target="_blank">Kakl</a>), a source of fresh and sometimes crazy ideas, and Jakub Kákona (<a href="https://github.com/kaklik" target="_blank">kaklik</a>), a young student passionate about radio astronomy and robotics. Together, they started designing new modules, writing articles, and managing the project's website.
    </p>
